Class ToolTipUI.Expandable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.spi.debugger.ui.ToolTipUI.Expandable
  • Enclosing class:
    ToolTipUI

    public static final class ToolTipUI.Expandable
extends Object
    Description of an expandable tooltip. The expanded tooltip is a view created from models registered under ToolTipView name. Default model filters are provided, which define the expanded first node with expression name and variable being the node's value.
